<br>
If a creature aggros on you it adds you to it's aggro list.  But if you get a certain distance away it will stop it's chase without you having to zone.  From that point on every creature of it's kind it passes will also add you to the list.  Using Selos you can out run the creature and if no one kills it before it passes frieds you can really build.  Skywise did a corpse recovery in Gfay and had two pawns aggro he out ran them but they never showed up to get him.  For the next hour until he logged every few seconds the faction gain message you get for killing an orc was scrolling across his chat screen.  It was quite nice. <p>Aegis Wolves Pack Master<BR>
Rochambeaux Warrior of Ralos Zek<BR>
